 P(W^c\cap X^c \cap Y^c \mid Z) = 1 - P\bigl((W^c \cap X^c \cap Y^c)^c \mid Z\bigr)
  = 1 - P(W \cup X \cup Y \mid Z) = 1 - P(W \mid Z) - P(X \mid Z) - P(Y \mid Z)
